## Deploy SSR with Vercel

When deploying Nuxt SSR with Vercel you need to add `.nuxt/dist/sitemap-routes.json` file as `serverFiles`. See the example below:

```js[vercel.json]
{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "nuxt.config.js",
      "use": "@nuxtjs/vercel-builder",
      "config": {
        "serverFiles": [
          ".nuxt/dist/sitemap-routes.json"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
```
